<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h2 style="color: #000099;">Reset Your Password</h2>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>You requested to reset your password. Use the OTP below:</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #000099;">
        <%= otp %>
      </span>
    </div>
    <p>This OTP expires in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br/>TruSkills Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>